      <title>瑞士立法者称瑞士央行可能继续忽视气候风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/snb-can-continue-to-ignore-climate-risks-swiss-lawmakers-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士议会称，瑞士央行在货币政策中不必考虑气候和环境风险。]]></description>
